Text: First off thanks for the upload, you're the only one on the planet nice enough to upload Red Eye.  Is it just my computer or has the video encoding been a bit rough lately?  It's Pixelated and multiple video drop outs lasting up to a minute.  Ah well still a good show; just need Lauren Sivan to burn down the leg chair with SE Cupp sometime...

Ive been playing around trying to get the quality up, by using a larger format, but maybe thats not working well. I think when I put it back though it looks fuzzy. I just havent found the best way to encode.
